    Class
    Description
    Applicant
     
    ApplicantController
     
    AuthApplicantService
    The AuthApplicantService class extends AuthService and provides the login functionality for applicants.
    AuthController
    The AuthController class provides utility methods for managing user authentication within the application.
    AuthHDBManagerService
    The AuthHDBManagerService class extends AuthService and provides the login functionality for HDB managers.
    AuthHDBOfficerService
    The AuthHDBOfficerService class extends AuthService and provides the login functionality for HDB officers.
    AuthService
    The AuthService class is an abstract class that implements the IAuthService interface.
    AuthStore
    The AuthStore class provides utility methods for managing the current authenticated user within the application.

    BTOApplicationStatus

    BTOApplicationView
    View class for displaying BTO application information
    BtomsApp
    The main class responsible for running the BTOMS application.

    BTOProjectAvailableView

    View class for managing project filters
    BTOProjectManagementService
     
    BTOProjectManagementView
    View class for BTO project management operations

    Service class for BTO project operations that can be used by both applicants and HDB officers
    BTOProjectView
     
    CommonView
     
    CsvDataService
    The CsvDataService class implements the IFileDataService interface and provides methods for reading and writing data from/to CSV files.
    DataStore
    The DataStore class provides utility methods for managing data storage within the application.
    Enquiry
    Model representing an enquiry from an applicant about a BTO project
    EnquiryService
    Service class for handling enquiry-related operations
    EnquiryView
     
    EnumParser
    Utility class for parsing enum values from display names
    FilePathsUtils
    The FilePathsUtils class provides utility methods for managing file paths within the application.
    FilterStore
    Store class for project filters This class stores filter settings for each user so they persist between menu pages
    FlatType
    Enumeration representing the types of BTO flats available
    FlatTypeDetails
    The FlatTypeDetails class represents the details of a flat type in a BTO project, including the number of units available and their selling price.

    HDBManagerController
    Controller for HDB Manager operations

    HDBOfficerController

    IAuthService
    The IAuthService interface defines a contract for managing authentication services, such as login and logout.
    IBTOProjectService
     
    IFileDataService
    The IFileDataService interface defines a contract for importing and exporting data to and from files.
    IProjectView
    The IProjectView interface defines a contract for displaying project information.
    IUserService
    The IUserService interface defines a contract for user services.
    MaritalStatus
    Enumeration representing marital statuses for BTO applicants
    ProjectFilter

    ProjectFilter.ProjectSortOrder
     
    RegistrationStatus
     
    ReportService
     
    ReportView
     
    TextDecorationUtils
    The TextDecorationUtils class provides utility methods for providing text decoration in the console display for the whole application.

    UserController
    The UserController class is responsible for handling user-related actions, such as changing the user's password.
    UserService
    The UserService class implements the IUserService interface and provides functionality related to user management, such as changing passwords.
    UserType
    Enumeration representing the types of users in the system
    WithdrawalRequest
